name: Dr. Raj Randhawa
about:
Dr. Raj Randhawa was born and raised in Edmonton, Alberta, where he developed a strong connection to his community. He completed his undergraduate studies at Concordia University before earning his dental degree with honors from Boston University. His dedication to excellence ensures that every patient receives high-quality, personalized care. 

Dr. Raj takes pride in providing exceptional dentistry with a focus on patient comfort and long-term oral health. He offers a wide range of services, including cosmetic dentistry, Invisalign, oral surgery, root canals, and children’s dentistry, addressing both routine and complex dental needs. 

Committed to lifelong learning, Dr. Raj continually advances his education to stay updated with the latest dental technologies and techniques. He believes in a patient-centered approach, emphasizing clear communication, gentle care, and customized treatment plans to help patients achieve healthy, confident smiles. 

Outside of dentistry, Dr. Raj enjoys spending time with his fiancée, family, and friends. Whether exploring new places or staying active, he values a balanced life. Proud to serve the Devon community, he looks forward to building lasting relationships with his patients.

clinic.name: Devon Dental Centre
clinic.description: Devon Dental Centre is a trusted dental clinic providing high-quality care in Devon, AB. Led by Dr. Raj, our clinic offers a full range of services, including preventive care, cosmetic dentistry, restorative treatments, and emergency dental care. We prioritize patient comfort and use modern technology to ensure the best possible experience. Whether you need a routine check-up, teeth whitening, or more advanced dental work, our friendly team is here to help. Experience personalized care in a welcoming environment—book your appointment today!
